<materialsCitation id="3B439843B748FFF6FAE6FC7BFABFF26E" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3805018324" pageId="15" pageNumber="122">“El Copey de Dota, in the Cordillera de Talamanca, Costa Rica ... 6000 feet [1829 m].”</materialsCitation>
